title: Bin El Ouidane
text: Bin El Ouidane is a small town and <a href="List%20of%20municipalities%2C%20communes%2C%20and%20arrondissements%20of%20Morocco">rural commune</a> in <a href="Azilal%20Province">Azilal Province</a>, <a href="B%C3%A9ni%20Mellal-Kh%C3%A9nifra">Béni Mellal-Khénifra</a>, <a href="Morocco">Morocco</a>. At the time of the <a href="2004%20Moroccan%20census">2004 census</a>, the commune had a total population of 5721 people living in 958 households.
